{"article_id":"CpnJvvCBRo4caeYV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Republicans voted Thursday to block President Obama 's immigration executive actions ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"though it was unclear whether the largely symbolic step would be enough","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to prevent a risky budget stand-off next week .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The House voted 219-197 for the bill , by Rep. Ted Yoho , R-Fla. ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"that declares Obama 's actions `` null and void and without legal effect . ''","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The legislation is part of a three-step plan by House GOP leaders","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to both address Obama 's immigration maneuvers","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"and approve a new spending bill","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"to avert a partial government shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Next week , the chamber is set to vote on a bill","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"funding most of the government through fiscal 2015 ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"and the Department of Homeland Security through early next year .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"That would tee up a new fight over funding for Obama 's immigration policies","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"when Republicans control both chambers .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"However , many conservative lawmakers want to wage that battle now ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and use the looming Dec. 11 deadline","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"-- when current government funding expires --","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"as leverage","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to defund the immigration plan .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"They worry","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Yoho 's legislation is an ineffective tool","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"for doing that ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"as the stand-alone bill","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"approved Thursday","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"stands little chance","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"of passing the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The White House also has issued a veto threat ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"calling the bill `` non-sensical . ''","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"`` I 'm not happy , ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Rep. Mick Mulvaney , R-S.C. , said .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"he 's concerned","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"if Republicans do n't fight the immigration policy now ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"it could send the wrong signal ahead of the new Congress .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Conservative sources indicate","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"there are between 30 and 40 , or more , conservatives","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"who would bolt on any spending bill next week .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"`` There 's a higher risk","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"of more [ members ] bolting , ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"said one source .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"`` Let us sort of vent .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"[ GOP leaders ] thought","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"this was going to be as big an issue . ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"despite that concern , one source said","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"GOP leaders think","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"would-be defectors will come back","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to favor the plan at the end .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Asked if he was concerned","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that opposition could torpedo the spending bill ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"House Appropriations Committee Chairman Hal Rogers , R-Ky. , said :","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"`` I do n't think so .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"I 'm hearing good things about it . ''","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Still , House Speaker John Boehner might need Democratic support","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"to carry the spending package across the finish line next week .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"who had been coy about whether she 'd help pass a spending plan ,","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"said Thursday","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"she 's reached out to Boehner","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"to extend a `` hand of friendship ''","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"to keep the government open","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"-- as long as Democrats see a bill","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"they can support .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"It 's unclear whether the legislation in the works meets that criteria .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"She indicated Thursday","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that Democrats might make demands","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"if Boehner needs their help .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"`` If he has 218 votes ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"there 's no conversation .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"If he does n't ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"we have leverage , ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"At a press conference earlier Thursday , Boehner urged his rank-and-file to be patient ,","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"making the case","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"for delaying the immigration fight until next year .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"`` Come January , we 'll have a Republican House and Republican Senate ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"and we 'll be in a stronger position","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"to take actions , ''","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"Boehner said","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"the current plan is `` the most practical way","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"to fight the president 's action . ''","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"Obama 's executive actions would defer deportations","depth":3},{"id":85,"text":"and grant work permits to up to 5 million illegal immigrants .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":171,"left":159,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":94,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","